Summary: Large craft high in the sky no sound disappeared with flash 6 lights on bottom oval shape.
divs: Sighting Detailsi was in bed asleep and i woke up. i was still a little tired but i know i wasnt dreaming. the window was open and for some reson i looked out it i dont know why but i did. i was in almost a transe like state. when i looked out the window i saw a disk like object with six lights on what looked like the bottom. the lights were in two rows of three lights. im not sure how high in the sky it was.it seemed to move slowly and then dissapered with a flash.i dont remember if there were was any sound. i felt no fear at all more just wonder. once it disapered i snaped out of the trance and relized what i had just seen. i got out of bead and sketched what i saw amd wrote down the time. sadly i didnt get the exact date. after i wrote down what i saw i just went back to bead. i know, how weird is that. i was not afraid of this craft at all! i added a copy of the sketchi drew.
